A [[holarchy|Holarchy]] of [[squads|Autonomous Squad]] and [[chapters|Chapter]] arranged into a set of [[Value Stream]]s is called a ''portfolio''. The usage is similar to {{SAFe}} portfolios or [[Spotify]] / {{Haudenosaunee}} tribes. 

XSCALE portfolios are limited in size by the [[Dunbar Number]]. Each [[continuously adapts|Continuous Adaptation]] its configuration of squads and chapters to its [[release plans|Release Plan]] and business objectives via a [[Portfolio Squad]]. 